<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MediaLab Arcade Template</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(168,85,247,0.22), transparent 24%), radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(34,211,238,0.18), transparent 28%), linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #0f172a 55%, #111827 100%); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
    <div id="arcade-hero" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 46px; top: 40px; width: min(1120px, calc(100vw - 92px)); height: 340px; border-radius: 40px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 44px 130px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.46);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 40px 44px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,14,39,0.94) 0%, rgba(49,46,129,0.94) 44%, rgba(8,145,178,0.88) 100%); color: #f8fafc;">
        <div style="max-width: 60%;">
          <div style="display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(34,211,238,0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.28); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #67e8f9;">Game Launch Site</div>
          <h1 style="margin: 18px 0 10px; font-size: 60px; line-height: 0.92; letter-spacing: -0.06em;">Neon Drift goes live at midnight.</h1>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(241,245,249,0.84);">A bold gaming landing page with esports energy, launch countdown styling, and strong trailer / wishlist call-to-action zones.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 26px; display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee 0%, #a855f7 100%); color: #020617; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;">Watch Trailer</a>
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); color: #f8fafc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;">Wishlist Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 290px; padding: 22px; border-radius: 30px; background: rgba(15,23,42,0.55); border: 1px solid rgba(103,232,249,0.18); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #a5f3fc;">Launch Stats</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 38px; font-weight: 900; color: #ffffff;">240K</div>
            <div style="font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">players on watchlist</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 12px;">
            <div style="padding: 12px; border-radius: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);"><div style="font-size: 11px; color: #c4b5fd; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em;">Mode</div><div style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Solo + Squad</div></div>
            <div style="padding: 12px; border-radius: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);"><div style="font-size: 11px; color: #67e8f9; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em;">Platform</div><div style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;">PC / Console</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="arcade-features" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 46px; top: 412px; width: min(1120px, calc(100vw - 92px)); height: 280px; border-radius: 34px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.28);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 16px; background: rgba(2,6,23,0.72); border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.14);">
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 26px; padding: 22px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34,211,238,0.16) 0%, rgba(15,23,42,0.84) 100%); color: #f8fafc;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #67e8f9;">Velocity</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 10px; font-size: 28px;">Zero-lag drift combat</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(226,232,240,0.86);">Fast-paced arena movement with clean reward loops and a cinematic HUD-inspired content layout.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 26px; padding: 22px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(168,85,247,0.18) 0%, rgba(15,23,42,0.84) 100%); color: #f8fafc;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c4b5fd;">Season Pass</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 10px; font-size: 28px;">Fresh drops every week</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(226,232,240,0.86);">Perfect for a premium launch page, pre-order campaign, or community waitlist with a louder visual edge.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 26px; padding: 22px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(14,165,233,0.18) 0%, rgba(15,23,42,0.84) 100%); color: #f8fafc;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #93c5fd;">Tournament</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 10px; font-size: 28px;">Built for stream hype</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(226,232,240,0.86);">Use this starter to announce competitions, highlight creators, and funnel traffic into your launch CTA.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="arcade-cta" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 46px; top: 726px; width: min(1120px, calc(100vw - 92px)); height: 210px; border-radius: 32px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 26px 80px rgba(8,145,178,0.2);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 30px 34px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #111827 38%, #164e63 100%); color: #f8fafc;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #67e8f9;">Launch CTA</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 12px 0 10px; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">Ready to publish your next game reveal page?</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(226,232,240,0.82);">Swap in your own title art, trailer embed, and community links, then export a dramatic landing page from the builder.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 200px; padding: 16px 22px; border-radius: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee 0%, #a855f7 100%); color: #020617; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 900;">Join the Drop</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
